  Photoresistor

  Turn a LED on by changing it brightness according to the values read by a photoresistor.
  Display the read values and the remapped values on the Serial Monitor.

  Input:
  1x Photo cell (CdS photoresistor)
  1x 10KΩ resistor
  Output:
  1x 5mm LED
  1x 560Ω resistor

